Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 好頭痛 簡直...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God, this headache, it just--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受 我的視線都模糊不清了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard. I can't really-- I can't see properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再播放一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can we play it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你記憶中一樣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that how you remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's different about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是用瑞典語交談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We weren't speaking Swedish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你完全不會說瑞典語嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you don't speak Swedish at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽得懂一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can kind of understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會 媽咪 我不會說瑞典語\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no, Mummy, I can't speak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你說的是英語\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The way I remember it, you were speaking English,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說到冷原子實驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you were talking about the CAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷原子實驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The CAL?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說他們在做一項實驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said that they were doing an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me that--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保羅在做一項實驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Paul was doing an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 問題是 我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thing is, Alice, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生意外前 我對冷原子實驗毫無印象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't remember the CAL before the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那項實驗毫無印象 我不...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't remember anything about it. I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不記得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't remember it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利說那個東西跟什么物理學有關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Henry said it was something to do with, like, physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.45,0:04:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一項量子實驗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a quantum experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要用來捕捉量子疊加形態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's supposed to capture a quantum superposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是量子疊加狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指同一件東西能同時出現在兩個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's sort of like when one thing can exist in two places at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個寫著你名字的卡帶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's another one with your name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的日期是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the date on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“2021年10月15日”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"10th of the 15th, 2021."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是意外發生后隔天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the date after the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休士頓 我想知道將尸體運返地球的流程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Houston, what are the protocols on dealing with a dead body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空站 你有什么擔憂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Station, what's your concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的擔憂是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My concern...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的擔憂是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The concern is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾利遜的傷口嚴重裂開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ericsson is so badly lacerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心尸體搬進救生艙后 一旦離開零重力...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My concern is that when the body gets out of zero-G--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許沒必要聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we don't need to listen to these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我只需要想個辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I just need to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 別擔心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be okay. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做些意大利面 然后一起抱抱 接著...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just gonna make some pasta for us. We could just cuddle up, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我跟以前一樣嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I the same to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的愛麗絲嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I your Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我... - 對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I... - Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 別這么說 你不用道歉 不是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, you mustn't be sorry, Alice. It's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得你不像我的媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't feel like you're my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不像你媽媽嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們必須想想辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we have to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是需要想想辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just-- We just need to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你通知艾琳娜了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you speak to Irena?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's on her way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她來干嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why is she on the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她會負責照顧你太太\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because she's the one who will take care of your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那你又來干嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And sorry, what are you doing here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那部機器對人有害無利 不是嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, your machine's no bloody good to anyone now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來是因為這事也曾發生在我身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here because this happened to me as well.
