Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 寶貝 說話啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, baby, talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么躲在櫥柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you hide in the cupboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 寶貝  - 我害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Baby? - I was scared.
