Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來像你的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You smell like you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然像誰的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else should I smell like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有點刺痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This might sting a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你很快就暖和起來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's gonna get you warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go. There you go.
