Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 你去了哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened? Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那邊 在外面的大雪中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's there, out in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從外面回來嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you been out there in the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見媽媽了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她找到我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今她又消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now she's gone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 如果你真看到她... 我知道你以為看到她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Honey, if you saw her-- I know you think you did--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是夢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受得到她的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到她的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I smelt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到雪的觸感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她剛剛就在那邊 - 她不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She was right there. - She wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 她剛剛就在那邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was. She was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒辦法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 趕緊讓你暖和起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Let's just get you warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回到床上睡覺 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get you back to bed, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 她在哪里  - 誰啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where is she? - Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到自己嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you see yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是指鏡子中嗎  - 不是 在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- In the mirror? - No! Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我什么都沒看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy, I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換衣服 那邊還有一間小木屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get dressed. There's another cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們的小木屋一樣 但不是我們的小木屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like our cabin, but it's not our cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟卡帶有關\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this about the tapes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊穿上雪地裝備 我們要過湖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put your snow gear on. We've got to go across the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我對我說過的話向你道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy, I'm sorry about what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我不是有意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy! I didn't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們趕緊回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. Let's just go back to how we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛剛躲在樓上的櫥柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was hiding in the cupboard upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了 她會凍死的 我們得趕緊找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's too cold. She'll freeze. We gotta find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情況\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.02,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路徹底堵住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The road's completely blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趕緊去弄個鏟雪機啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, get a digger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm not waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒被困在另一邊 我太太瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My daughter's stuck out there, and my wife's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪 我覺得另一間小木屋不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy, I don't think there is another cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定是這個方向\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think-- I think--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人難過時可能會看到幻象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People can see things sometimes when they're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些到過外太空的人都會看到幻象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People who have been to space before have seen things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想傷害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't wanna hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不想讓你難過 但我認為你說得對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really don't wanna make you upset, but I think you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你不是我的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think you're my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果我不是你的女兒 那你又是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, if I'm not, then who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我媽咪做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What have you done to my mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起找出真相吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's find out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了 我要爸爸 我要回家找爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're crazy! I want Daddy! I want to go home to Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 別跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 別跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.52,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 又來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Christ. Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mamma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mamma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到另一間小木屋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've found the other cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.07,0:23:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽咪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.65,0:25:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.15,0:25:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 你聽得到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, can you hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.38,0:25:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 你聽得到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, can you hear this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.94,0:26:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果聽得到 就說點什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can hear this, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.07,0:26:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果聽得到 就說點什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you can hear this, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.17,0:26:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.00,0:26:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.61,0:26:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.57,0:26:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.08,0:27:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.66,0:27:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 如果你不在屋里 我就要報警了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, if you're not here, I'm gonna have to call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.04,0:27:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是愛麗絲嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.42,0:27:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.39,0:27:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在小木屋里 在樓上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At the cabin. Kind of. Upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.43,0:27:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.07,0:27:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的小木屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it our cabin?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.74,0:27:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點像我們的小木屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like our cabin...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.70,0:27:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在櫥柜里嗎  - 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you in the cupboard? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.17,0:27:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.59,0:28:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是不同的櫥柜吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not the same cupboard, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們是同一個愛麗絲嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're the same Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.54,0:28:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.87,0:28:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊有一面鏡子嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there a mirror there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.17,0:28:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.67,0:28:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你往鏡子里看 我也會往鏡子里看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you look in, I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 我們被反鎖在里面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit. We've locked ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.23,0:28:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.52,0:28:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把自己反鎖在里面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've locked ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.53,0:29:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.57,0:29:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會說英語嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.87,0:29:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒失蹤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My daughter is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.08,0:29:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在阿爾梅道北部的一間小木屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in a cabin on the north side of ?lmedalen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.29,0:29:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她十歲大 請你們馬上到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She-She's ten years old. I need you to come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跑到湖面上了 安全嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone out on the lake. Is that safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她往湖面走去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's where she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.53,0:29:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她認為這樣能找到她媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She thinks she can find her mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得到什么嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.61,0:30:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.45,0:30:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是一樣的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are we the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.54,0:30:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里干嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.88,0:30:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找我媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looking for my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.25,0:30:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見到她了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you seen her?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.59,0:30:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.80,0:30:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跑來把我拉出櫥柜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She came and took me out of this cupboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.93,0:30:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個櫥柜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This cupboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.01,0:30:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.43,0:30:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你住在小木屋里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you staying at the cabin?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.56,0:30:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.48,0:31:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽跟你住在一起嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is your mamma staying there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.86,0:31:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.20,0:31:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.99,0:31:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.70,0:31:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.79,0:32:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.59,0:32:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.01,0:32:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她什么時候死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When did she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.97,0:32:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她死在外太空 到現在還在太空站里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In space. She's still up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.35,0:32:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是跟你說瑞典語\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she speak Swedish with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.06,0:32:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.77,0:32:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家的車是什么顏色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What color is your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.73,0:32:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.03,0:32:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽也死了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is your mamma dead too?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.70,0:32:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你的媽媽還活著 但我的媽咪已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's your mamma who's alive and my mummy who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.08,0:32:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們好像交換了位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think they swapped places.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.34,0:32:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.43,0:32:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把她還給我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I have her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.00,0:33:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么病 是精神崩潰嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was it, like a breakdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.04,0:33:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我坐在指揮艙里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was up there on the command module.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛從月球返回地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just come back from the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.09,0:33:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回航進入第16個小時后 艙內發生失壓事故\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sixteen hours in, there was a depressurization.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.30,0:33:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兩個船員...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.14,0:33:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來 他們已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It looked to me like they were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.18,0:33:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整個人也失去意識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I kinda blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.39,0:33:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復意識后 奇跡發生了 他們倆都好好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The miracle happened when I came to, they were okay again.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.19,0:33:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到地球后 我卻病了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I came back to Earth, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.57,0:33:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那你是怎么好起來的  - 我吃了藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So, how'd you get better? - I took the pills...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.78,0:33:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后用工作麻痹自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I threw myself into my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.49,0:33:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多久才康復\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how long did it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.95,0:34:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路通了 要不要跟來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're ready. You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.63,0:34:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.59,0:34:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 愛麗絲 - 愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Alice! - Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.57,0:35:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.02,0:36:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.87,0:36:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.12,0:36:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.17,0:36:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個說瑞典語的愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the one who speaks Swedish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.04,0:36:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we need to--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.88,0:36:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.30,0:37:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got Mamma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.89,0:37:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在櫥柜里嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the cupboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.10,0:37:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 她就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.27,0:37:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.65,0:37:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽不到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.52,0:37:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.53,0:37:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們只能通過我對話了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you have to speak through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.46,0:37:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.88,0:37:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.22,0:37:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利 我要去找你算賬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm coming to get you, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.31,0:37:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲早會找上你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.27,0:37:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會來找你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.52,0:37:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 到時我會把世界搞得天翻地覆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And boy, am I gonna fuck things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.49,0:38:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.20,0:38:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.04,0:38:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.96,0:38:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.68,0:38:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.11,0:38:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.83,0:38:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.33,0:38:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says she loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.71,0:39:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.72,0:39:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能通過鏡子看到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I see her in the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.51,0:39:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.52,0:39:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.85,0:39:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得見我說話嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.69,0:39:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她聽不見你說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.95,0:39:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她問你什么時候回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says, "When are you coming home?"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.00,0:39:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我回不回得去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know if I can come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.59,0:39:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她不知道她回不回得去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says she doesn't know if she can come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.76,0:39:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.34,0:39:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Becau-- Because I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.31,0:39:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎么回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know how to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.14,0:40:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能需要想想辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might-- I just need to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.65,0:40:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說我會想辦法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell her I will work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.73,0:40:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道怎么回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.78,0:40:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她需要想想辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She just needs to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.24,0:40:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會想辦法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.64,0:40:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.47,0:40:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德拉指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Caldera?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.35,0:40:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫我巴德吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I prefer Bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 慢著 等一下 亨利 你聽我說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on, wait, wait, wait, wait, Henry, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.35,0:40:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.52,0:40:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒用那個名字 我不叫亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't use that name. My name is not Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.75,0:41:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.26,0:41:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.67,0:41:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.72,0:41:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.76,0:41:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好困\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.35,0:41:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.23,0:41:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.98,0:41:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.27,0:41:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.28,0:41:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 跟我說話啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.29,0:41:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.18,0:42:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 告訴我怎么回事 - 這就是真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell me what happened. - This is what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.31,0:42:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 放開我 - 我是不會上當的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fucking hands off-- - I'm not taking shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.69,0:42:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我滾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德拉指揮官 告訴我你怎么會在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Caldera, you tell me why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.53,0:42:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你怎么會在這里  - 別開槍 等等 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why the fuck are you here? - No, wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.18,0:42:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Henry! Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.98,0:42:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 帶她走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here, take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.65,0:42:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找我女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've gotta find my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.04,0:43:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.63,0:43:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保羅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.13,0:43:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保羅 我是亨利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Paul! It's Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.13,0:43:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 別暈過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Jesus Christ. Oh, God. You stay with me. You stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.68,0:43:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.90,0:43:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,911 快派救護車過來 有人中槍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}911? They need an ambulance. It's a gunshot wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.36,0:43:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 腹部中槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, to the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.53,0:43:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 地址 該死的地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Address. Goddamn address.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.91,0:43:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉磯 在洛杉磯的某處 什么...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Los Angeles. Los-Los Angeles somewhere. What--
