Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.00,0:43:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我的眼鏡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christ, my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.25,0:43:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60...保羅 別暈過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}60-- Stay with me, Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.71,0:43:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊辛頓大道 郵區號60556\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}60556 Lexington Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.09,0:43:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.13,0:44:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡德拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Caldera.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.55,0:44:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.77,0:44:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 你到底是誰啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who the fuck are you, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.49,0:44:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.95,0:44:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只穿著內衣褲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just in my underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.54,0:44:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.71,0:44:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.05,0:44:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.18,0:45:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.81,0:45:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice. Alice. Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.81,0:45:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.07,0:45:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.66,0:45:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.33,0:45:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.42,0:45:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你做過一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I made you one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.19,0:46:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須救救她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.15,0:46:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.78,0:46:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mamma?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.49,0:46:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我已經感覺不到她的存在了 - 沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can't feel her anymore. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.12,0:46:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像已經死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.21,0:46:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 快醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.05,0:46:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.84,0:46:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.27,0:46:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.32,0:47:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去爸爸那邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.70,0:47:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我才是你的愛麗絲啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm your Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.91,0:47:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.08,0:47:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去爸爸那邊 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Papa. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.47,0:47:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jo?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.89,0:47:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you, Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.27,0:47:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.77,0:47:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.15,0:47:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.66,0:47:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.50,0:48:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.96,0:48:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.97,0:48:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.97,0:48:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.43,0:48:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.85,0:48:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the fuck did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.39,0:48:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.39,0:48:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰  剛剛有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who was-- Were you with someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.77,0:48:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.53,0:48:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 沒事的 來 有我在 你怎么樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Okay. Come here. I got you. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.70,0:48:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.37,0:48:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.59,0:48:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.09,0:48:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice, baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.72,0:49:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice! Alice! Alice! Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.90,0:49:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.23,0:49:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再這樣對我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not do that to me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.19,0:49:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.28,0:49:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后別再這樣對我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.28,0:49:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我看見媽媽了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I saw Mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.99,0:49:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫我回到你身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She told me to come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.75,0:50:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你沒看到她嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.46,0:50:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛有沒有看到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.79,0:50:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I--
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.42,0:50:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.27,0:51:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.69,0:51:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.44,0:51:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想見媽媽嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to see your mamma?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.12,0:51:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來 我帶你去找媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me, and I'll take you to your mamma.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.92,0:51:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.88,0:51:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就在不遠的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's not far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.92,0:51:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.80,0:51:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.01,0:51:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子 走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come away, child.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.52,0:51:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.86,0:51:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 我在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.49,0:51:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.37,0:52:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.04,0:52:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去尋求治療了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone to get help.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.79,0:52:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who for?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.21,0:52:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.88,0:52:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不應該讓你們單獨相處的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should never have let you be alone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.59,0:52:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟誰走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who did she go away with?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.05,0:52:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫艾琳娜拉森科的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A woman called Irena Lysenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.35,0:52:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是宇航員嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A cosmonaut?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.85,0:52:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.77,0:52:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.12,0:52:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得把她帶回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to get her back.
